3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a decentralized scheme for coded caching, which can be considered a control system. 
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper proposes a method for partitioning the encoding set, which can be considered a distributed computing problem. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with coded-multicasting, which is a technique used in multimedia applications.
